{"tid":1333988,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[721] 唔好睇小灣仔地形","createTime":"2019-07-20T03:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T04:48:41.000Z","uid":281948,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58dd3c321217544f96fcdc49bf9383d2481bf0e0","tid":1333988,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"灣仔地勢, 有利警方佈防<br />\n<br />\n灣仔警方有機會好似上次沙田咁, 提早節龍, <br />\n咁西面仲有大量遊行人士, <br />\n前線無得向西退就只有南北兩邊散開, <br />\n北面情況, 詳情請睇 #獅子山下龜頭上  的分析<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[721置頂] 警犬部署分析</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333423</a><br />\n<br />\n想補充<br />\n灣仔南面, <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">皇后大道中</span></span></strong>以南都是好斜的大斜路<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>南固台</strong></span></span>會改建成酒店, 而家是個大地盤<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>賽馬會公園</strong></span></span> 黃色的highlight 全是無路可行的大斜坡<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">日, 月, 星街</span></span></strong> 上左去又是死路, 無出口<br />\n灣仔無大型商場, 即是一入店舖就是死路, <br />\n都無天橋, 全是地面窄路戰<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方只要推我地去南面再慢慢收網就傷亡慘重</span></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n絕不建議兄弟們於灣仔開戰, 無論如何都要BE WATER, 沉住氣<br />\n<br />\n相反, <br />\n要知道, <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港文華東方酒店</span></span></strong> + <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>香港置地文華東方酒店</strong></span></span> 入住的人, 都是非富則貴, 不是大機構的BOSS , 就是好話到事的管理層, 多是工幹旅遊的富貴人家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>置地廣塲, 置地太子, 置地遮打, 歷山大廈, 太子大廈, 環球商場, 中匯大廈, 全都有天橋連接</strong></span></span>, 我唔確定地契有無定明要24 hrs 開放, 但一般寫字樓都會預租客隨時可返office 做野, 所以, 正常地下, 2 樓(因為有天橋), 都可以自由出入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">中國會</span></strong></span>, 唔講食一餐幾錢, 單是會費, 一年10 萬, 仲要有人放先入到會, 有錢都未必買到, 你話畀食飯的大粒佬親身睇到個遊行會幾震撼<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">太子大廈</span></span></strong>的Sevva 望出去的景<br />\n<br />\n另外,  香港公園開放時間, 每日上午6時至晚上11時, 入面好大, 好多路, 又有電梯落返去太古廣場<br />\n<br />\n遮打花園南面長江公園開24 hrs, 附近都是大大小小的天橋連接"},{"pid":"0c15d204703b23dd886296fe191d2f9ed962f298","tid":1333988,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7735aed538b5a5d9375ce0de1c8549207e4c82f","tid":1333988,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"我未打完, 唔小心send 左出黎<br />\n有無得再修改架?"},{"pid":"bd89484c0f749315b5ce7ae708038d83c57059d7","tid":1333988,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7735aed538b5a5d9375ce0de1c8549207e4c82f","tid":1333988,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"我未打完, 唔小心send 左出黎<br />\n有無得再修改架?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"冇，重開啦"},{"pid":"2e8d5fa963846f3069f3265686c3a44d72350364","tid":1333988,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7735aed538b5a5d9375ce0de1c8549207e4c82f","tid":1333988,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"我未打完, 唔小心send 左出黎<br />\n有無得再修改架?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔好用藍色 黑夜mode睇得好唔舒服"},{"pid":"7c1f25ed877621ec111a50caed524cf31eb1631c","tid":1333988,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:19:38.000Z","msg":"新手唔知, 下次唔用藍色,<br />\n另外, 用咩色比較好?"},{"pid":"d12f463a8a9ee5fb9a61e77cf94181a9949418ee","tid":1333988,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"